String.string: Reinforcements approach. Don't let them overwhelm you!
Archers behind the bulwark! Take out the leaders!
The wardstone protects you from all damage for 20 seconds.
Rubinaria rushes to gather her young.
Smash the wardstone to prevent being overwhelmed.
Rubinaria weakens when her mate dies.
Namburus strengthens Rubinaria when he stands beside her.
Saravash will unleash his wrath in 15 minutes.
A caprin imp summons a spirit.
No more crystals will appear. Kill Saravash quickly.
